    <h4 class="h3">I don’t like the taste of artificial sweeteners</h4>

    <p>Some people report an “aftertaste” when drinking beverages sweetened with artificial sweeteners. Several no calorie sweeteners are currently on the market, including NutraSweet, Splenda, and Stevia. Try sugar-free beverages with these different sweeteners to find one that you like.</p>

